discourse_list.title: [S15 Voter's Guide] Compendium of Voter's Guides

content.content: Season 15 is here, and voting is now live for a number of workstreams. Lots of stewards are putting together voter’s guides. I want to offer my guide here for these interested, and ideally turn this into a single thread where others can post their guide. I will work to add each newly published guide to this first post to prevent lots of scrolling through the thread.  Kyle’s Voter’s Guide Annika’s Voter’s Guide Lindsey’s Voter’s Guide Nate’s Voters Guide  Happy voting and thanks again to the workstreams for the immense work this season (yet again!).

These are really comprehensive, look like a TON of work, and I would find very useful to understand the budget proposals.  I also appreciate the transparency where there could be a perceived conflict of interest and the resulting abstinence.  Thank you.
